<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto+Mono:wght@200;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"> 
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css">
    <title>PlayerToo</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header">
        <nav class="flex navBase">
            <ul class="flex navList">
                           
            </ul>
            <div>
                <a class="simpleBtn lightGreen" href="/auth/discord">Login</a>
            </div>
            
        </nav>        
    </header>
    <section class="flex logoContainer">
        <img class="floating mainLogo" src="assets/cropped-shiny-logo.png" alt="">
    </section>
    
    <ol class="howToList">
        <li class="infoBox">
            <h2 class="headerText">How to use PlayerToo</h2>
            <p class="parText">Use PlayerToo to find friends around your skill level in games. We use hours in game to determine who would be a good match for your PlayerToo!</p>
        </li>
        <li class="infoBox">
            <h2 class="headerText lightGreen">1. Log in with your Discord account</h2>
            <p class="parText lightGreen">Log in with your Discord account and authorize the PlayerToo application.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="infoBox">
            <h2 class="headerText">2. Find your favorite games</h2>
            <p class="parText">Go to the search tab and look for your favorite games.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="infoBox">
            <h2 class="headerText lightGreen">3. Add yourself to the list</h2>
            <p class="parText lightGreen">Add yourself to the list by entering the number of hours you have in the game. </p>
        </li>
        <li class="infoBox">
            <h2 class="headerText">4. Find Friends</h2>
            <p class="parText">Once added, you will see a list of players with the same amount of experience in game as you.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="infoBox">
            <h2 class="headerText lightGreen">5. Add friends</h2>
            <p class="parText lightGreen">Reach out to the player on Discord to set up a time to play together. After all, they were looking for a PlayerToo.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>
    <div class="center loginContainer">
        <div class="loginSection flex">
            <a class="loginButton headerText lightGreen" href="/auth/discord">Log In</a>
        </div>
    </div>
        

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>Website designed and built by: <a class="navLink footerLink" href="https://github.com/Hazelwize" target="_blank">Micah Jackson</a> </p>
    </footer>
   

    
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>